oupled DM halos are consistent with the\nobserved scaling relation between the core radius $r_0$ and core density\n$\\rho_0$, in terms of an universal core surface density $\\rho_0\\times r_0$\namong different galaxies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 7 Feb 2021 18:21:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-07"}
