y defined by Ashtekar\nand Wilson-Ewing. Finally, we highlight certain features that simplify this\nreduced embedding problem, but which may not have direct analogues in the\nembedding of homogeneous and isotropic loop quantum cosmology into full loop\nquantum gravity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 7 Feb 2021 20:06:56 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 16 Jul 2021 23:11:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-08"}
