lves into elongated streamwise vortices on higher\naspect ratio wings, while on shorter wings it becomes indistinguishable from\ntip-vortex instability.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 8 Feb 2021 10:12:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-13"}
