how that Ba$_3$Sn$_2$ has Weyl\npoints with an accordion dispersion and topological nodal planes, while AuBr\nand Tl$_4$PbSe$_3$ possess Dirac points with hourglass dispersions. For each of\nthese candidate materials we present the ab-initio band structures and discuss\npossible experimental signatures of the nontrivial band topology.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 8 Feb 2021 11:22:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-02"}
